{"tid":1660101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵指高鐵售票系統故障 乘客只可購買2小時内出發車票","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T10:31:09.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbb4a87071f77d2588a74156fa230349837bd01","tid":1660101,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"港鐵宣布，由於售票系統故障，影響到高鐵售票系統的售票及取票服務，現時乘客只可以在香港西九龍站售票櫃位購買未來兩小時内出發車次的車票。已訂購車票的乘客，可以到香港西九龍站的售票櫃位辦理取票手續。工程人員正處理有關情況，有進一步詳情會通知大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1115782/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8C%87%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E5%94%AE%E7%A5%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%AF%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B72%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%86%85%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E8%BB%8A%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1115782%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2594%25AE%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2595%2585%25E9%259A%259C-%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B72%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2586%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A5%25A8&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=d3accd57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1115782%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2594%25AE%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2595%2585%25E9%259A%259C-%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B72%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2586%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A5%25A8&h=7c6c08e